Interface ManualTransmission

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    RegularManualTransmission

    public interface ManualTransmission
    This interface is used for classes that will simulate a car transmission. This includes methods to return the speed and gear of the transmission, as well as commands to increase and decrease both. There is an option to output a status to show whether the input command was carried out successfully.
